Ideas for PPO to test
1. sharpe ratio based on 1 week capital on lower time frame like 1 hour
b) sharpe ratio based on 1 month capital on higher time frame like 1 day
2. walk forward testing
3. use of different reward functions like sharpe ratio, sortino ratio, calmar ratio, omega ratio, etc
4. higher penalty for negative returns
5. use of different activation functions like tanh, relu, etc
6. use of different optimizers like adam, rmsprop, etc
7. use of different loss functions like mse, mae, etc
